snippet.title: Kung Fu Clicker: Announcement trailer
snippet.description:
PikPok presents Kung Fu Clicker! 

Train students in the arts of kung fu and recruit martial arts masters in Kung Fu Clicker, the idle fighting game!

The dreaded Shadow Fang gang are wreaking havoc in the neighborhood! Fight to defend your dojo, compete against other kung fu clans, and climb the leaderboards to earn rewards and win glory for your clan!

Be the first to hear when Kung Fu Clicker is available! 

Subscribe, and follow us:
On Facebook at http://www.facebook.com/pikpokgames/
Join the Kung Fu Clicker community: https://www.facebook.com/groups/KungFuClicker/
On Twitter @PikPokGames and join the conversation with #KungFuClicker
